40 yadā vayam duḥkhārtaṃ mārgaṃ pravartāmahe;
41 ata eva vraṇāni punaḥ samyuktaṃ bhavanti
42 pūrvam eva yasya agre anyaḥ āgacchati.

46 "Na mṛtyuḥ enam adyāpi prāptaḥ, na pāpaḥ enam nayati,"
47 pratyavādat mama guruḥ, "tam vadhitum;
48 api tu tasmai pūrṇam anubhavam dātum,

49 mama, yaḥ mṛtaḥ asmi, enam netum ucitam
50 narake 'smin adhastāt paryāya paryāyeṇa;
51 etad eva satyam yathā aham tava bruve."

61 Tataḥ kadācid ekena pādena gamanāya udgataḥ,
62 Mamadamukhena Muḥammadaḥ idam vacas cakāra;
63 tataḥ sthale viśrāntāya sa viṣṭabdhaḥ.

88 sa tāṃstameva samālocanāya ānayisyati;
89 tataḥ saivam kariṣyati yathā Focārā-vāte
90 na teṣāṃ vratam na prārthanā vāpi kāryā syāt.

109 Ahaṃ ca tatra abravam: "Tava vaṃśasya ca mṛtyuḥ";
110 Yataḥ saḥ duḥkham duḥkhena samuccayya,
111 Duḥkhī vikṣiptaśca puruṣa iva jagāma.

112 Aham tu tiṣṭhāmi paśyantaḥ samūham,
113 Paśyāmi ca vastūni yāni śrutvā,
114 Api kevalam varṇayitum bibhemi;

118 Aham khalu apaśyam, athavā adhunāpi paśyāmi,
119 ekam kāyam śiraḥ-rahitaṃ gacchantam yathā
120 anye api gacchanti sma duḥkhitasya paśavoḥ;

124 Sa svayam eva ātmānaḥ prakāśaḥ āsīt,
125 ca dvau ekena ca ekena dve;
126 katham etad bhavati, sa eva jānāti yaḥ evam niyamati.

